data.description: Welcome to 6877 Ridgevue Drive in South Park! This beautiful home in a peaceful neighborhood offers comfort, style, and lovely views. It has spacious living areas, perfect for family get-togethers and entertaining friends. The kitchen is well-equipped with appliances, plenty of storage, and a nice breakfast nook with big windows for scenic views. The house has updated roofing, gutters, flooring, and HVAC.    You'll also enjoy the scenic South Park views from your large private corner lot, and the outdoor space is great for relaxation and outdoor fun. The home is conveniently located in the South Park School District, just a short distance from parks, schools, shopping, and dining options. There's also an attached garage for your convenience and extra storage.    Don't miss the chance to make this lovely South Park property your new home!
